
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
}


<div class="cd-dashboard provider">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl">Course Directory</span>
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl cd-dashboard-title">Migration Report</h1>
    <hr class="spacer" />



    <div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-body">

        <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
            <p>
                We have transferred your data to the new course directory.
            </p>
            <p>
                To help you make sure your current provision is published correctly on the new course directory we have produced a report for you with actions you need to take.
            </p>
            <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
                Alternatively, you can overwrite any data transfer and ensure all of your provision is up to date by

                <a asp-controller="AddCourse" asp-action="BulkUpload" class="govuk-link">uploading a file of all your courses</a>.
            </p>

            <div class="govuk-!-margin-top-9 cd-migration-report-item">
                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">17 courses successfully transferred </h2>
                <a asp-controller="Courses" asp-action="CourseListfullwidth6" class="govuk-link">View</a>
                <p>You need to check the information you had on the previous course directory was correct and delete any courses you no longer run.</p>

                <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">12 courses not transferred </h2>
                @*<a href="#" class="govuk-heading-m"><strong>12</strong>  </a>*@
                <h3 class="govuk-heading-s"><strong>9</strong> No or expired LARS/QAN</h3>

                <p>If you still run these courses you will need to publish them to the new course directory.</p>
                <h3 class="govuk-heading-s"><strong>3</strong> Courses with errors</h3>
                <p>You can still publish these courses if you <a asp-controller="Migration" asp-action="FixErrors" class="govuk-link">Fix errors</a> first. If you no longer run the courses, <a href="#">our helpdesk can delete them</a>.</p>


                <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--visible" />
            </div>

            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="index" class="govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-6">Continue to course directory</a>
        </div>

    </div>

</div>

